    <div class="art-tile tall" data-img="/art/dp.webp" data-caption="Deadpool (2018) - This was my first piece exploring with colored pen.">
      <img loading="lazy" src="/art/dp.webp" alt="Roots I" />
    </div>
    <div class="art-tile" data-img="/art/purp.webp" data-caption="Entrapta (2021) — Unfinished piece exploring markers and pen.">
      <img loading="lazy" src="/art/purp.webp" alt="Echoes" />
    </div>
    <div class="art-tile" data-img="/art/spider.webp" data-caption="Study: Spider-Man (2025) — A current work in progress.">
      <img loading="lazy" src="/art/spider.webp" alt="Study" />
    </div>
    <div class="art-tile tall" data-img="/art/nwing1.webp" data-caption="Nightwing (2020) — Extending into some color highlights.">
      <img loading="lazy" src="/art/nwing1.webp" alt="Migration" />
    </div>
    <div class="art-tile tall" data-img="/art/papa.webp" data-caption="Papa (2024) — Recreated three of my favorite images with my father for a birthday gift. Used alcohol markers and mulberry papers for the first time.">
      <img loading="lazy" src="/art/papa.webp" alt="Early Sketch" />
    </div>
    <div class="art-tile tall" data-img="/art/hulk.webp" data-caption="Hulk (2016) — Pencil on paper. First art piece I gifted a friend.">
      <img loading="lazy" src="/art/hulk.webp" alt="Early Sketch" />
    </div>
    <div class="art-tile tall" data-img="/art/cap.webp" data-caption="Captain America (2017) — I still struggle with drawing faces but the hardest part of this piecce was drawing the scales on his suit.">
      <img loading="lazy" src="/art/cap.webp" alt="Early Sketch" />
    </div>
    <div class="art-tile" data-img="/art/fish.webp" data-caption="Koi (2020) — I am not good with paint but did this cute piece with a friend.">
      <img loading="lazy" src="/art/fish.webp" alt="Early Sketch" />
    </div>
    <div class="art-tile tall" data-img="/art/flash.webp" data-caption="Flash (2016) — This is when I started exploring dynamic images.">
      <img loading="lazy" src="/art/flash.webp" alt="Early Sketch" />
    </div>
     <div class="art-tile tall" data-img="/art/bouquet.webp" data-caption="Small Bouquet (2025) — i am practicing my flower sketches for an eventual tattoo design.">
      <img loading="lazy" src="/art/bouquet.webp" alt="Early Sketch" />
    </div>
    <div class="art-tile" data-img="/art/stitch1.webp" data-caption="Angel and Stitch (2021) — A valentines gift with my favorite, Stitch.">
      <img loading="lazy" src="/art/stitch1.webp" alt="Early Sketch" />
    </div>
    <div class="art-tile" data-img="/art/stitch2.webp" data-caption="Angel and Stitch (2021) — Simple classroom sketches lead to the idea of making them as gifts.">
      <img loading="lazy" src="/art/stitch2.webp" alt="Early Sketch" />
    </div>
    <div class="art-tile" data-img="/art/stitch3.webp" data-caption="Angel and Stitch (2021) — I love paper crafts and would like to incorporate them more for more depth in my pieces.">
